#Author: persist
#Abstract: explain what system.sfs(system.img) does

Structure
.
├── app
├── bin
├── build.prop
├── etc
├── fonts
├── framework
├── lib
├── lib64
├── lost+found
├── media
├── priv-app
├── usr
├── vendor
└── xbin

Pack
make_ext4fs -T file_contexts -l 1024M -a system system.img system/
mksquashfs system.img system.sfs

Unpack
simg2img system.img  system.img.ext4
mkdir system
mount -t ext4 -o loop system.img.ext4 system

Key

